      <title>迟来的数据显示外国投资者逃离中国股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/foreign-investors-flee-chinese-shares-long-delayed-data-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年，外国投资者持有的中国股票数量连续第二年下降，原因是市场低迷导致持股价值下降，投资者纷纷转向其他地方寻求更高回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/foreign-investors-flee-chinese-shares-long-delayed-data-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
