      <title>印度官员表示，随着需求激增，煤炭产量需要增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/coal-output-needs-to-rise-as-demand-jumps-indian-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位负责监管燃料的政府重要官员称，印度国营矿业公司印度煤炭有限公司将继续增加产量，以满足不断增长的需求并帮助增加库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/coal-output-needs-to-rise-as-demand-jumps-indian-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:31:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
